0N 115W       34  X   X( X)   X( X)   X( X)   X( X)   X( X)   3( 3)\n \n$$                                                                  \nFORECASTER BUCCI                                                    \n\n</pre>','\n',char(10)),NULL,'','2023-11-01 20:41:02','Eastern Pacific Basin Tropical Cyclones','',NULL,'2023-11-02 00:10:14','read');
